---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage configuration

Usage: mf config [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  schema    Show config schema
  show      Show effective config
  compile   Compile config (alias of show)
  generate  Generate effective config file
  default   Show default config values
  init      Initialize config file (mf extension)

Options:
      --root <PATH>
          Mind Repo root directory
      --config <PATH>
          Config file path
  -v, --verbose...
          Verbose output
  -q, --quiet
          Silence non-error output
      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --json
          Shorthand for --format json
      --no-color
          Disable colored output
      --install-completion <INSTALL_COMPLETION>
          Install shell completion script [possible values: bash, zsh, fish, powershell, elvish]
      --show-completion <SHOW_COMPLETION>
          Show shell completion script [possible values: bash, zsh, fish, powershell, elvish]
  -h, --help
          Print help
  -V, --version
          Print version
